main event: Two teenage boys in Cheyenne, Wyoming observed a round UFO moving rapidly from southwest to northeast on May 28, 1966.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for about 5 minutes before the object disappeared.,No sound was associated with the sighting.,A second observation reported a different group of men seeing a similar object moving erratically.,Weather was clear during the sightings.,The observers were able to estimate the size of the object using a dime and a 25-cent piece held at arm's length.
witness description: two teenage boys and two men
